1
00:00:24,980 --> 00:00:28,500
♪Heavens strike with thunderous wrath♪

2
00:00:28,700 --> 00:00:32,180
♪Mountains and rivers shatter before my eyes♪

3
00:00:32,420 --> 00:00:35,500
♪Endless splendor cultivated through lifetimes♪

4
00:00:35,780 --> 00:00:39,220
♪Turns to dust between my fingers in an instant♪

5
00:00:40,540 --> 00:00:44,100
♪When the line between good and evil is clear♪

6
00:00:44,220 --> 00:00:47,780
♪Countless souls drift into the boundless wilds♪

7
00:00:48,340 --> 00:00:51,340
♪Carrying the spirit fire forward♪

8
00:00:51,500 --> 00:00:53,340
♪I defy fate♪

9
00:00:53,580 --> 00:00:56,460
♪Just to remain by your side♪

10
00:00:57,340 --> 00:01:00,740
♪Falling into love's abyss♪

11
00:01:01,180 --> 00:01:04,420
♪Like heavy rain pouring down♪

12
00:01:04,860 --> 00:01:08,300
♪Drunk on romance♪

13
00:01:08,460 --> 00:01:11,980
♪In a blink, love and hate vanish into illusion♪

14
00:01:12,700 --> 00:01:16,060
♪Falling into endless love♪

15
00:01:16,500 --> 00:01:19,340
♪Stirring waves upending a lifetime♪

16
00:01:19,620 --> 00:01:22,420
♪Even if this life leads to ruin♪

17
00:01:22,860 --> 00:01:26,460
♪I still choose to be entangled with you♪

18
00:01:27,020 --> 00:01:30,100
♪Through all lifetimes♪

19
00:01:30,100 --> 00:01:33,100
[When Destiny Brings The Demon]

20
00:01:33,100 --> 00:01:36,500
[Based on the JJWXC novel "When Destiny Brings The Demon" by Fu Hua]

21
00:01:36,540 --> 00:01:39,500
[Episode 5]
[The Key Player and Survivor in the Grandmaster's Revenge Plan]

22
00:01:39,720 --> 00:01:40,530
Master Yin,

23
00:01:40,670 --> 00:01:41,810
why haven't the elders

24
00:01:41,830 --> 00:01:43,250
from your palace come back yet?

25
00:01:43,750 --> 00:01:45,090
Could it be that I was right,

26
00:01:45,360 --> 00:01:47,530
and the Grandmaster's spiritual power hasn't weakened?

27
00:01:47,910 --> 00:01:50,420
Everyone, keep calm.

28
00:01:51,080 --> 00:01:52,700
Just wait patiently.

29
00:02:03,960 --> 00:02:06,010
Do you remember what I taught you?

30
00:02:08,710 --> 00:02:10,090
Where should you stab for the best effect?

31
00:02:21,670 --> 00:02:22,410
Do it.

32
00:02:28,040 --> 00:02:28,690
Do it!

33
00:02:30,080 --> 00:02:31,850
Why are you all forcing me to do things?

34
00:02:39,270 --> 00:02:39,900
Boss,

35
00:02:40,670 --> 00:02:42,130
are you trying to frame me?

36
00:02:51,760 --> 00:02:52,570
No...

37
00:03:10,590 --> 00:03:11,500
I've killed someone.

38
00:03:12,990 --> 00:03:14,090
I've killed someone.

39
00:03:40,830 --> 00:03:42,460
The spirit vein really has weakened.

40
00:03:42,830 --> 00:03:43,500
Perfect chance!

41
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:46,340
You're not getting ahead of me.

42
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:54,650
Madam Xing,

43
00:03:55,670 --> 00:03:56,690
aren't you going in?

44
00:03:58,320 --> 00:03:59,090
Sect Master Shi,

45
00:04:00,200 --> 00:04:01,940
you are the Grandmaster's guardian.

46
00:04:02,480 --> 00:04:03,570
If even you are not going in,

47
00:04:04,150 --> 00:04:05,620
how could I act rashly?

48
00:04:06,920 --> 00:04:08,370
You were there

49
00:04:08,390 --> 00:04:10,250
when the Grandmaster was sealed.

50
00:04:11,320 --> 00:04:13,340
You know better than anyone how powerful he is.

51
00:04:14,270 --> 00:04:17,540
Is it true his spiritual power weakens on the night

52
00:04:17,790 --> 00:04:18,770
of the new moon?

53
00:04:20,790 --> 00:04:21,770
I don't know.

54
00:04:22,680 --> 00:04:26,980
But I don't think the Grandmaster will allow himself to be prey.

55
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:30,010
Grandmaster, wake up.

56
00:04:31,350 --> 00:04:32,010
Grandmaster.

57
00:04:32,150 --> 00:04:32,860
Grandmaster?

58
00:04:33,350 --> 00:04:33,980
Wake up!

59
00:04:35,230 --> 00:04:35,980
Grandmaster!

60
00:04:39,590 --> 00:04:40,620
You're noisy.

61
00:04:41,880 --> 00:04:43,010
Are you all right?

62
00:04:55,590 --> 00:04:56,250
Scared?

63
00:04:57,030 --> 00:04:58,010
Of course I'm scared.

64
00:04:58,710 --> 00:05:00,210
I've never even killed a chicken,

65
00:05:00,760 --> 00:05:02,370
and you told me to kill you.

66
00:05:03,150 --> 00:05:04,980
Why did you run into my blade?

67
00:05:06,830 --> 00:05:07,500
Relax.

68
00:05:08,470 --> 00:05:12,180
It's just a necessary step to break the seals.

69
00:05:12,760 --> 00:05:14,060
What do you mean?

70
00:05:22,390 --> 00:05:23,980
The real show is about to start.

71
00:05:26,440 --> 00:05:26,980
Grandmaster,

72
00:05:27,230 --> 00:05:28,570
how did you end up so badly injured?

73
00:05:28,910 --> 00:05:29,500
Grandmaster,

74
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:31,060
are you well?

75
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:35,180
The one next to the Grandmaster.

76
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:36,660
You.

77
00:05:38,230 --> 00:05:39,250
Check his pulse.

78
00:05:41,230 --> 00:05:42,100
How do I do that?

79
00:05:42,590 --> 00:05:44,130
I've never studied Traditional Chinese Medicine.

80
00:05:56,680 --> 00:05:57,660
No need to check.

81
00:05:57,910 --> 00:05:58,890
Just look at him.

82
00:05:59,520 --> 00:06:01,010
He's clearly at his limit.

83
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:05,890
Indeed.

84
00:06:08,390 --> 00:06:09,890
I am gravely wounded,

85
00:06:10,880 --> 00:06:12,980
and my spiritual power is almost gone.

86
00:06:14,590 --> 00:06:16,770
I suppose that's why

87
00:06:17,910 --> 00:06:19,180
you've all shown up.

88
00:06:19,960 --> 00:06:21,010
Everyone is here, huh?

89
00:06:23,200 --> 00:06:24,180
Good.

90
00:06:27,830 --> 00:06:29,210
I am right here.

91
00:06:31,760 --> 00:06:32,740
Come and take my life.

92
00:06:37,790 --> 00:06:38,420
Grandmaster,

93
00:06:38,790 --> 00:06:40,420
where is this confidence coming from?

94
00:06:41,710 --> 00:06:43,740
I almost killed you earlier,

95
00:06:44,590 --> 00:06:46,450
and now we're facing death together?

96
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:51,570
If I don't let you die,

97
00:06:52,760 --> 00:06:53,740
you won't die.

98
00:06:55,790 --> 00:06:56,740
Sima Jiao,

99
00:06:57,880 --> 00:07:00,010
even now, you're still so arrogant.

100
00:07:01,520 --> 00:07:04,250
We sent our disciples here to serve you out of goodwill,

101
00:07:05,150 --> 00:07:07,130
yet you killed them without cause.

102
00:07:07,230 --> 00:07:08,180
Why?

103
00:07:08,640 --> 00:07:10,060
Which palace are you from?

104
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:12,540
After being locked away by you for 500 years,

105
00:07:14,080 --> 00:07:15,500
I can hardly tell you people apart.

106
00:07:17,560 --> 00:07:19,450
Of those old fools who sealed me back then,

107
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:23,420
why are there only three of you here?

108
00:07:26,350 --> 00:07:27,620
Without everyone present,

109
00:07:28,200 --> 00:07:30,180
how can my desire for revenge be satisfied?

110
00:07:32,470 --> 00:07:34,540
He's picking a fight even now?

111
00:07:35,680 --> 00:07:36,810
He's really something else.

112
00:07:37,150 --> 00:07:38,250
I'm impressed.

113
00:07:38,520 --> 00:07:39,180
Everyone,

114
00:07:39,470 --> 00:07:40,810
you all heard him, right?

115
00:07:41,200 --> 00:07:43,620
Sima Jiao wants to settle old scores with us.

116
00:07:44,080 --> 00:07:45,370
If we join forces tonight,

117
00:07:45,590 --> 00:07:46,860
we can finish him.

118
00:07:47,320 --> 00:07:48,620
If we let him live,

119
00:07:48,960 --> 00:07:50,420
he'll kill us all sooner or later.

120
00:07:52,390 --> 00:07:54,540
Fools. Absolute fools.

121
00:07:56,830 --> 00:07:57,620
If I die,

122
00:07:58,390 --> 00:08:00,420
there will be no one left to sustain the Spirit Fire.

123
00:08:01,200 --> 00:08:02,420
Are you sure you want that?

124
00:08:04,520 --> 00:08:05,690
Once you are dead,

125
00:08:06,680 --> 00:08:09,420
with the Bloodseal Bloom and your corpse in our hands,

126
00:08:09,790 --> 00:08:13,010
we can still protect everyone in the Gengchen Celestial Palace.

127
00:08:20,880 --> 00:08:24,810
By Bloodseal Bloom, do you mean this?

128
00:08:51,680 --> 00:08:52,300
It's a trap!

129
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:54,850
Sima Jiao lured us here

130
00:08:54,920 --> 00:08:56,210
to use our blood to break the seals.

131
00:08:56,750 --> 00:08:57,260
Run!

132
00:09:06,990 --> 00:09:07,970
Where are you going?

133
00:09:08,470 --> 00:09:09,210
It's the Spirit Fire!

134
00:09:09,750 --> 00:09:10,610
We're trapped.

135
00:09:11,280 --> 00:09:11,780
Grandmaster,

136
00:09:12,160 --> 00:09:13,330
this must be a misunderstanding.

137
00:09:13,510 --> 00:09:14,570
We have no ill intent.

138
00:09:14,920 --> 00:09:16,020
At least we of the Heaven Palace

139
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:18,140
mean no disrespect to you.

140
00:09:18,830 --> 00:09:19,570
So it's true.

141
00:09:20,080 --> 00:09:22,330
Your supposed weakness on the night of the new moon was a lie.

142
00:09:22,590 --> 00:09:24,140
You're only realizing that now?

143
00:09:24,470 --> 00:09:25,570
Far too late.

144
00:09:26,630 --> 00:09:27,610
Let's fight him!

145
00:09:31,740 --> 00:09:37,620
♪All beings are but fleeting mayflies, deceived♪

146
00:09:38,780 --> 00:09:42,180
♪Only with both love and hate can one fight relentlessly♪

147
00:09:42,260 --> 00:09:50,380
♪To forge the boundless Great Way as its creator♪

148
00:09:52,300 --> 00:09:55,020
♪Rewrite the starry tides of time♪

149
00:09:55,060 --> 00:09:57,500
♪Dye the moon and sky in crimson light♪

150
00:09:58,320 --> 00:09:59,090
Sima Jiao,

151
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:00,780
your cruelty is beyond measure.

152
00:10:01,160 --> 00:10:03,850
You are a devil!

153
00:10:04,230 --> 00:10:05,140
Sima Jiao,

154
00:10:05,470 --> 00:10:07,090
may you die a miserable death!

155
00:10:07,630 --> 00:10:08,610
Sima Jiao,

156
00:10:08,750 --> 00:10:10,180
for all your scheming,

157
00:10:10,320 --> 00:10:13,420
you never expected Xing Hecan to be absent, did you?

158
00:10:13,420 --> 00:10:15,660
♪So what if we perish?♪

159
00:10:15,680 --> 00:10:17,660
Only the blood from the direct bloodlines

160
00:10:17,680 --> 00:10:19,850
of all Eight Palaces can break the seals.

161
00:10:20,560 --> 00:10:22,850
Xing Hecan has always been a coward,

162
00:10:23,230 --> 00:10:25,450
but that cowardice just ruined your plan.

163
00:10:25,710 --> 00:10:28,300
I would say that counts as a great service!

164
00:10:30,230 --> 00:10:31,730
What makes you think

165
00:10:32,680 --> 00:10:35,300
missing one person would doom my plan?

166
00:10:46,710 --> 00:10:48,060
Of course I've made good use

167
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:52,140
of the people you sent in.

168
00:12:12,320 --> 00:12:14,060
At last, the moment has come.

169
00:12:50,680 --> 00:12:51,300
Grandmaster,

170
00:12:51,830 --> 00:12:52,850
are you all right?

171
00:12:56,280 --> 00:12:58,180
I have endured these cursed seals

172
00:13:01,080 --> 00:13:01,940
long enough.

173
00:13:15,620 --> 00:13:21,140
♪If I could become a mortal being♪

174
00:13:21,420 --> 00:13:25,100
♪Forget the grudges of past lives, and feel neither joy nor sorrow♪

175
00:13:25,140 --> 00:13:28,820
♪I'd bear no resentment or regret♪

176
00:13:29,660 --> 00:13:34,380
♪Let my mortal heart fall to the human world♪

177
00:13:35,020 --> 00:13:41,180
♪I'll trade it for a lone, fearless self and let the past drift away♪

178
00:13:42,260 --> 00:13:48,940
♪With every regret I once held onto♪

179
00:13:49,020 --> 00:13:54,340
♪I'll survive countless trials and tribulations♪

180
00:13:56,100 --> 00:14:01,580
♪Let my mortal heart sink into the sea♪

181
00:14:01,860 --> 00:14:07,820
♪I dream of a weightless self, soaring to the heavens♪

182
00:14:08,420 --> 00:14:11,820
♪Neither alive nor gone, I'm bound only by endless loneliness♪

183
00:14:11,860 --> 00:14:15,380
♪Watching the world change♪

184
00:14:15,460 --> 00:14:27,820
♪Yet still unable to see through the long night♪

185
00:14:28,960 --> 00:14:29,780
Grandmaster,

186
00:14:31,280 --> 00:14:33,490
so we've broken the seals, right?

187
00:14:38,110 --> 00:14:38,780
Correct.

188
00:14:42,080 --> 00:14:42,810
Good to hear.

189
00:15:13,590 --> 00:15:14,970
The seals have actually been broken.

190
00:15:15,400 --> 00:15:16,020
I knew it.

191
00:15:16,800 --> 00:15:18,610
The claim that his power would weaken was a lie.

192
00:15:19,040 --> 00:15:21,420
If the Grandmaster spread that rumor, he must have had a plan.

193
00:15:21,560 --> 00:15:23,060
There must be a sea of blood up there now.

194
00:15:23,080 --> 00:15:23,780
Enough.

195
00:15:23,960 --> 00:15:24,610
Let's go and check.

196
00:15:33,160 --> 00:15:34,540
Look at them.

197
00:15:35,400 --> 00:15:37,610
Each one would be a figure to be feared outside.

198
00:15:41,630 --> 00:15:43,380
But look at them now.

199
00:15:46,710 --> 00:15:47,570
How pathetic.

200
00:15:52,750 --> 00:15:54,330
What are your thoughts on this?

201
00:15:58,440 --> 00:15:59,780
Your waist is so slim.

202
00:16:00,230 --> 00:16:00,810
What?

203
00:16:01,040 --> 00:16:02,690
I think you must have been locked away too long

204
00:16:02,710 --> 00:16:03,730
and starved into this shape.

205
00:16:08,590 --> 00:16:09,780
You are not wrong.

206
00:16:10,800 --> 00:16:12,140
The pain I've endured will be repaid.

207
00:16:13,350 --> 00:16:14,730
Every bit of it.

208
00:16:14,990 --> 00:16:16,330
That's not what I meant.

209
00:16:27,680 --> 00:16:29,380
Master Yin!

210
00:17:05,600 --> 00:17:06,620
Grandmaster,

211
00:17:07,360 --> 00:17:09,490
does this mean I don't have to be buried with you?

212
00:17:09,990 --> 00:17:11,050
Do you not want to die?

213
00:17:12,070 --> 00:17:13,420
Of course not.

214
00:17:15,510 --> 00:17:17,380
I was nearly scared to death just now.

215
00:17:21,880 --> 00:17:22,340
Come on.

216
00:17:23,440 --> 00:17:23,860
Hurry.

217
00:17:26,600 --> 00:17:27,450
The Grandmaster is out.

218
00:17:27,990 --> 00:17:29,290
Come on.

219
00:17:39,030 --> 00:17:41,420
Welcome back from seclusion, Grandmaster!

220
00:17:42,120 --> 00:17:44,340
Welcome back from seclusion, Grandmaster!

221
00:17:46,920 --> 00:17:49,100
Liao Tingyan, your neglect in service

222
00:17:49,400 --> 00:17:50,860
nearly brought ruin to the sect's lifeblood.

223
00:17:51,440 --> 00:17:52,100
Grandmaster,

224
00:17:52,270 --> 00:17:54,730
allow me to cleanse the sect for you today!

225
00:17:55,990 --> 00:17:56,620
Oh, no...

226
00:17:59,510 --> 00:18:01,450
Grandmaster, please forgive him.

227
00:18:03,990 --> 00:18:05,940
How dare you act with such impudence before me?

228
00:18:07,790 --> 00:18:08,620
Spare me, Grandmaster.

229
00:18:09,030 --> 00:18:10,380
I was only concerned for you.

230
00:18:12,990 --> 00:18:13,620
What are you afraid of?

231
00:18:14,200 --> 00:18:14,820
I told you,

232
00:18:16,750 --> 00:18:17,730
if I don't let you die,

233
00:18:18,310 --> 00:18:19,290
you won't die.

234
00:18:25,310 --> 00:18:27,290
Is this disciple from the Four Seasons Palace?

235
00:18:27,990 --> 00:18:29,730
Why has she earned such favor from the Grandmaster?

236
00:18:29,960 --> 00:18:32,770
I've never seen her before either.

237
00:18:33,600 --> 00:18:35,660
He slaughtered the disciples

238
00:18:35,750 --> 00:18:37,970
we sent into the mountain without hesitation.

239
00:18:38,600 --> 00:18:40,860
Why is he keeping this low-level,

240
00:18:40,880 --> 00:18:42,820
three-spiritual-root disciple?

241
00:18:43,440 --> 00:18:44,210
What use could she be?

242
00:18:44,510 --> 00:18:47,100
You know perfectly well what you were thinking

243
00:18:48,270 --> 00:18:49,380
when you sent in the disciples

244
00:18:49,840 --> 00:18:50,970
in the first place.

245
00:18:51,120 --> 00:18:51,660
You!

246
00:18:53,550 --> 00:18:54,140
Grandmaster,

247
00:18:55,790 --> 00:18:58,580
with the Three Saints Mountain in ruins,

248
00:18:59,680 --> 00:19:02,770
why don't you stay at White Deer Cliff for now?

249
00:19:03,230 --> 00:19:05,580
Once the disciples have repaired this place,

250
00:19:05,600 --> 00:19:06,940
we will invite you back.

251
00:19:06,960 --> 00:19:09,100
You plan to drag me back and seal me for another 500 years?

252
00:19:10,470 --> 00:19:11,900
That's not what I meant, Grandmaster.

253
00:19:12,310 --> 00:19:12,690
I just...

254
00:19:12,710 --> 00:19:13,290
Enough.

255
00:19:26,880 --> 00:19:27,580
Grandmaster,

256
00:19:28,710 --> 00:19:30,290
you're not going to kill me

257
00:19:30,310 --> 00:19:31,380
because I saw you

258
00:19:32,310 --> 00:19:33,420
kill someone, right?

259
00:19:48,790 --> 00:19:49,690
What are you thinking?

260
00:19:50,440 --> 00:19:52,210
If you want to kill me, go ahead.

261
00:19:52,920 --> 00:19:54,210
Stop playing with my mind.

262
00:19:55,990 --> 00:19:57,140
If you're tired of killing,

263
00:19:58,550 --> 00:20:00,770
why not wash up and get some sleep?

264
00:20:03,750 --> 00:20:04,620
Very well.

265
00:20:15,990 --> 00:20:16,690
Sect Master Shi,

266
00:20:16,790 --> 00:20:18,660
what does the Grandmaster intend by this?

267
00:20:39,120 --> 00:20:39,690
Boss...

268
00:20:41,710 --> 00:20:42,450
Grandmaster,

269
00:20:42,640 --> 00:20:43,580
I still want to live.

270
00:20:43,710 --> 00:20:45,380
Please don't kill me.

271
00:20:45,750 --> 00:20:46,900
Then I will spare your life.

272
00:21:11,840 --> 00:21:13,420
I didn't see it coming at all.

273
00:21:25,710 --> 00:21:26,530
Is that so?

274
00:21:27,880 --> 00:21:31,770
Well, I have prepared for that moment for 500 years.

275
00:21:33,550 --> 00:21:35,420
I have always known I would need the blood

276
00:21:36,160 --> 00:21:37,770
of the direct bloodlines of the Eight Palaces

277
00:21:39,710 --> 00:21:41,290
to break the seals and barriers.

278
00:21:41,990 --> 00:21:43,050
The challenge was

279
00:21:43,710 --> 00:21:46,140
gathering the blood from all eight bloodlines.

280
00:21:48,440 --> 00:21:49,490
I could not leave,

