She's also feeding the Spirit Fire with her blood,

556
00:39:48,320 --> 00:39:50,050
just like the Grandmaster.

557
00:39:50,630 --> 00:39:51,860
When I come tomorrow,

558
00:39:52,760 --> 00:39:54,530
will I catch you in a good mood?

559
00:39:54,960 --> 00:39:56,530
I've never taken my temper out on you.

560
00:39:56,960 --> 00:39:58,860
It's the other Sima clan members

561
00:39:58,990 --> 00:40:00,220
who keep annoying me.

562
00:40:00,760 --> 00:40:02,420
So she's a member of the Grandmaster's clan.

563
00:40:03,140 --> 00:40:04,280
[Zichen Hall]

564
00:40:04,280 --> 00:40:07,170
This looks like White Deer Cliff in the past.

565
00:40:07,440 --> 00:40:09,420
Sima E, stop being so stubborn.

566
00:40:10,070 --> 00:40:10,780
I don't want to marry him.

567
00:40:11,190 --> 00:40:11,970
I will not marry him!

568
00:40:12,590 --> 00:40:14,450
Preserving the pure bloodline of the Fengshan line

569
00:40:14,670 --> 00:40:15,340
to feed the Spirit Fire

570
00:40:15,530 --> 00:40:17,160
- is the Sima clan's mission. - Her again?

571
00:40:17,800 --> 00:40:19,700
Then I must have entered her memory.

572
00:40:19,880 --> 00:40:20,780
But I don't love him.

573
00:40:20,920 --> 00:40:21,530
Nonsense.

574
00:40:21,670 --> 00:40:24,260
How can the clan's mission be weighed against personal feelings?

575
00:40:24,590 --> 00:40:26,570
You and Sima Shi are of the same clan but different branches.

576
00:40:26,990 --> 00:40:29,340
You were born to bear the duty of continuing the Fengshan line.

577
00:40:30,030 --> 00:40:32,170
This marriage follows both propriety and custom.

578
00:40:32,470 --> 00:40:33,940
You're forcing me to marry and bear children?

579
00:40:34,550 --> 00:40:35,970
It must be the Eight Palace heads' idea again.

580
00:40:36,320 --> 00:40:37,220
Look at us now.

581
00:40:37,590 --> 00:40:39,780
Do we still look like we are in charge of the Celestial Palace?

582
00:40:40,280 --> 00:40:41,130
We are nothing

583
00:40:41,470 --> 00:40:43,570
more than puppets to keep the Eight Palaces' glory alive.

584
00:40:43,670 --> 00:40:46,010
This concerns the prosperity and stability of the Celestial Palace.

585
00:40:46,360 --> 00:40:48,420
E, stop being so obstinate.

586
00:40:48,550 --> 00:40:49,260
Get out!

587
00:40:49,760 --> 00:40:51,700
Leave now, or I will burn you alive!

588
00:40:52,920 --> 00:40:56,260
How tragic. She has no freedom to choose whom to marry,

589
00:40:56,990 --> 00:40:57,970
is constantly manipulated,

590
00:40:57,990 --> 00:40:59,490
and shoulders the fate of an entire clan.

591
00:41:04,960 --> 00:41:07,130
But why would the Eight Palaces

592
00:41:07,150 --> 00:41:08,650
stoop to forcing marriages for heirs?

593
00:41:09,630 --> 00:41:10,610
How is a life like this

594
00:41:12,630 --> 00:41:14,820
any different from being a caged bird?

595
00:41:15,280 --> 00:41:16,340
As long as I exist,

596
00:41:16,470 --> 00:41:18,970
the fate of the Sima clan will never change.

597
00:41:19,470 --> 00:41:20,970
People's greed has pushed us

598
00:41:22,280 --> 00:41:23,780
to the brink of despair.

599
00:41:24,190 --> 00:41:25,260
If one day,

600
00:41:25,720 --> 00:41:27,450
the Fengshan Spirit Fire ceases to exist,

601
00:41:28,110 --> 00:41:29,220
the Sima clan

602
00:41:29,840 --> 00:41:31,170
might finally be free.

603
00:41:34,840 --> 00:41:38,260
But now, the Grandmaster is still feeding the Spirit Fire.

604
00:41:43,240 --> 00:41:44,260
A wedding?

605
00:41:47,070 --> 00:41:48,780
She gave in after all.

606
00:42:08,400 --> 00:42:10,300
Marriage should be a willing,

607
00:42:10,630 --> 00:42:11,780
joyful thing,

608
00:42:12,920 --> 00:42:15,220
yet here it feels so suffocating.

609
00:42:16,280 --> 00:42:19,380
Today, Sima Shi and Sima E are joined as partners

610
00:42:19,720 --> 00:42:22,090
to continue the bloodline of Fengshan

611
00:42:22,630 --> 00:42:25,570
and nourish the Spirit Fire!

612
00:42:33,280 --> 00:42:35,010
The Eight Palaces are truly revolting.

613
00:42:35,590 --> 00:42:36,450
I can't believe

614
00:42:36,800 --> 00:42:37,650
the Sima clan

615
00:42:37,670 --> 00:42:39,380
