616
00:42:44,440 --> 00:42:45,380
Where am I now?

617
00:42:47,470 --> 00:42:48,130
There...

618
00:42:48,440 --> 00:42:48,900
E,

619
00:42:49,590 --> 00:42:52,220
give our child a name.

620
00:42:55,110 --> 00:42:56,490
Let's call him Jiao.

621
00:42:58,800 --> 00:43:01,170
This baby is actually the Grandmaster?

